slip 6 stitches to right hand needle; k1; then pass each slipped stitch over the knit stitch and drop off the needle, p2; then one by one lift the second, third, fourth, fifth, sixth and seventh stitches on the left hand needle over the first and off the needle; knit the first stitch [the stitch that the other stitches were lifted over], p5
